    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300026534_5_1936-1975",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1936-1975",
      "markText": "如今持续性流行病多存在于被称为“全球南方”（Global South）的地区。",
      "totalCount": 42,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300026534&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1936&rangeEnd=1975",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee832a30813ab70ddg0149ff?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1936&rangeEnd=1975"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300026534_6_11920-11950",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "11920-11950",
      "markText": "政府采取上述所有以及其他措施来控制疫病，有时近乎残暴和铁腕。",
      "totalCount": 39,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300026534&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=11920&rangeEnd=11950",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee832a30813ab70ddg0149ff?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=11920&rangeEnd=11950"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300026534_6_2916-3011",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2916-3011",
      "markText": "人们从几个方面对病因给出了解释：天意、瘴气、接触传染、个人易感性等等，这些病因说互相有交集。就和霍乱流行一样，这些解释（特别是瘴气和接触传染）直到19世纪末期仍然在疾病传播理论中占统治地位。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300026534&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2916&rangeEnd=3011",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee832a30813ab70ddg0149ff?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2916&rangeEnd=3011"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300026534_6_8882-8959",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "8882-8959",
      "markText": "政府开始对人们和货物采取隔离措施，颁布旅行禁令，禁止宗教游行等公众集会，将患者和疑似病人纳入更有力的政府控制之下，这些举措表明传染理论得到了（部分）认可。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300026534&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=8882&rangeEnd=8959",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee832a30813ab70ddg0149ff?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=8882&rangeEnd=8959"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300026534_6_4278-4300",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "4278-4300",
      "markText": "在欧洲有多达1000个犹太社区被暴徒们摧毁。",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300026534&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4278&rangeEnd=4300",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee832a30813ab70ddg0149ff?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4278&rangeEnd=4300"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300026534_6_11782-11805",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "11782-11805",
      "markText": "1910年中国东北境内暴发了一种致命的肺鼠疫。",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300026534&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=11782&rangeEnd=11805",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee832a30813ab70ddg0149ff?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=11782&rangeEnd=11805"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300026534_6_14434-14476",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "14434-14476",
      "markText": "政府以前所未有的力度介入和干预印度人民的生活，并以1897年《传染病法案》的颁布告终",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300026534&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=14434&rangeEnd=14476",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee832a30813ab70ddg0149ff?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=14434&rangeEnd=14476"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300026534_6_14642-14728",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "14642-14728",
      "markText": "这些政策——熏蒸和焚烧房屋；强制将病人送往不顾种姓习俗、人人畏惧的医院；禁止举办葬礼；对死者进行尸检；严格隔离病人等等——引发了19世纪印度历史上对西方医学最大规模的抵制。",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300026534&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=14642&rangeEnd=14728",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee832a30813ab70ddg0149ff?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=14642&rangeEnd=14728"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300026534_6_424-469",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "424-469",
      "markText": "它是由鼠疫杆菌引发、由带病的跳蚤——跳蚤在动物宿主死亡后会寻找人类宿主——叮咬传播的疾病。",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300026534&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=424&rangeEnd=469",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee832a30813ab70ddg0149ff?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=424&rangeEnd=469"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300026534_11_674-737",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "674-737",
      "markText": "已知最早的疫病于1918年3月5日在美国堪萨斯的芬斯顿营地暴发，随后传播到其他要塞和军事基地。4月病毒出现在开往法国的客船上。",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300026534&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=674&rangeEnd=737",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee832a30813ab70ddg0149ff?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=674&rangeEnd=737"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300026534_11_2285-2315",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "2285-2315",
      "markText": "西萨摩亚的损失最惨烈：几星期内3800万居民中有22%死亡。",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300026534&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=2285&rangeEnd=2315",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee832a30813ab70ddg0149ff?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=2285&rangeEnd=2315"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300026534_5_473-514",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "473-514",
      "markText": "人们往往只有在重新遭遇当代流行病时才会回望历史，如此曾经的模式在不经意间一再重演。",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300026534&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=473&rangeEnd=514",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee832a30813ab70ddg0149ff?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=473&rangeEnd=514"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300026534_3_1485-1527",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1485-1527",
      "markText": "随着人类的迁移、贸易和殖民活动，“微生物一体化”导致了疾病尤其是传染病的全球性扩散。",
      "totalCount": 28,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300026534&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1485&rangeEnd=1527",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee832a30813ab70ddg0149ff?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1485&rangeEnd=1527"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300026534_7_8734-8822",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "8734-8822",
      "markText": "活体天花病毒现在只存在于机密实验室中，在冷战期间它被美国和前苏联藏匿了起来。但在2014年6月，人们在美国国立卫生研究院的废弃仓库里发现了两瓶被遗忘数十年的活体天花病毒DNA。",
      "totalCount": 28,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300026534&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=8734&rangeEnd=8822",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee832a30813ab70ddg0149ff?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=8734&rangeEnd=8822"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300026534_8_9259-9313",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "9259-9313",
      "markText": "但在尼日利亚、莫桑比克等地大量蚊帐被人们改成了渔网。在捕鱼填饱肚子和蚊帐防蚊之间，几百万人都选择了填饱肚子。",
      "totalCount": 28,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300026534&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=9259&rangeEnd=9313",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee832a30813ab70ddg0149ff?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=9259&rangeEnd=9313"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300026534_3_632-683",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "632-683",
      "markText": "传染病是微生物与人类相互作用的结果。微生物是地球上最古老的生命之一，也伴随着人类的进化与大流行病的肆虐",
      "totalCount": 26,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300026534&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=632&rangeEnd=683",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee832a30813ab70ddg0149ff?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=632&rangeEnd=683"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300026534_6_6371-6417",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "6371-6417",
      "markText": "鼠疫可能将科技发展的步伐往前推了一百多年。风车和水车等动力设施发展迅猛，枪械的使用也是如此。",
      "totalCount": 26,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300026534&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6371&rangeEnd=6417",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee832a30813ab70ddg0149ff?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6371&rangeEnd=6417"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300026534_8_2609-2646",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "2609-2646",
